text: Diadelia brunneofasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1943.BioLib.cz - Diadelia brunneofasciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1943 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
